-- Pacific Rubiales Obtains $700 Million Revolving Credit Facility
-- B y   M a t t h e w   B r i s t o w
-- 2012-09-28T12:49:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-28/pacific-rubiales-obtains-700-million-revolving-credit-facility.html
Pacific Rubiales Energy Corp. (PRE) 
obtained a revolving credit facility for $400 million and a
second facility totaling $300 million in Colombian pesos, the
company said in a statement distributed yesterday by PR
Newswire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Matthew Bristow in Bogota at 
